'''''Dantooine's Pride''''' was a passenger liner aboard which the [[Force vampire|Force Vampire]] took refuge after he had escaped his prison on the [[Outrider-class cruiser|''Outrider''-class cruiser]] which the [[Order of the Silver Jedi]] had trapped him on. He never killed any passengers on board, though he did feed lightly on some of them, instead taking his major "meals" from residents of the [[Planet/Legends|planets]] the [[Starship/Legends|ship]] visited. The ''Pride'' was known to have made at least four stops in different systems with the Force Vampire on board. The ship was headed for the planet [[Coruscul]] when a team of investigators boarded it looking for the murderer of the Vampire's previous victims.

